parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leak through the windshield cowl can cause electrical components to fail, leading to overheating, and failure of the air conditioning system, dashboard features, and air compressor. This can result in a loss of critical vehicle functions, creating a safety risk and unpleasant driving experience.
symptoms: Water leaks into the cabin through the windshield cowl
water runs down the window to the dashboard
water drips onto the air compressor
mold and mildew growth under the dashboard
and failure of the air conditioning system.
